  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your survival ingenuity in four unique biomes—Woodland, Woodland Lake, Alpine Tundra, & Mountain—, all while imbibing charming pixel art, chill music, and thought-provoking quotes along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/ea2f4b45dadc7bfe386942a90fbc73b4.poster.avif?t=1768954112\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/ea2f4b45dadc7bfe386942a90fbc73b4.webm?t=1768954112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/ea2f4b45dadc7bfe386942a90fbc73b4.mp4?t=1768954112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE & SURVIVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each biome contains unique flora, fauna, and challenges. Players will need to hunt, trap, and gather to survive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CRAFTING SYSTEM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine gathered items by trial and error to produce tools that aid in survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/7e1d01cdcd5794dd06b58b2fff09bf41.poster.avif?t=1768954112\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/7e1d01cdcd5794dd06b58b2fff09bf41.webm?t=1768954112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/7e1d01cdcd5794dd06b58b2fff09bf41.mp4?t=1768954112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STRATEGIC SURVIVAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay warm and well fed in any season by stocking up, making smart decisions, and crafting key items.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNFOLDING MYSTERY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who built the abandoned shelters and left behind letters containing survival clues? And why?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/6fdb846924eee3a810f159088e1ffa53.poster.avif?t=1768954112\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/6fdb846924eee3a810f159088e1ffa53.webm?t=1768954112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/6fdb846924eee3a810f159088e1ffa53.mp4?t=1768954112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>INSPIRED MUSIC</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repeat-worthy instrumental tracks written to capture the spirit of each biome.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LITERARY QUOTES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ponder the thoughts of some of America’s best 19th- and 20th-century writers, philosophers, and poets during the nighttime loading screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/033ee4bdfe88c9e3ed4ba71e23f487b3.poster.avif?t=1768954112\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/033ee4bdfe88c9e3ed4ba71e23f487b3.webm?t=1768954112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/033ee4bdfe88c9e3ed4ba71e23f487b3.mp4?t=1768954112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INFORMATIVE JOURNAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn interesting facts about the flora, fauna, and tools you interact with.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  <strong>BEAUTIFUL WORLD & USER INTERFACE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro pixel art in delightful hues pair with contemporary game effects and design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/dd9cd338f7eb2331f40b2a79ac2adcf7.poster.avif?t=1768954112\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/dd9cd338f7eb2331f40b2a79ac2adcf7.webm?t=1768954112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/351730/extras/dd9cd338f7eb2331f40b2a79ac2adcf7.mp4?t=1768954112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
